@inherits RazorSharpEmail.EmailTemplate<Exceptionless.Core.Mail.Models.UserModel>

We heard you need a password reset. Click the link below and you'll be redirected to a secure site from which you can set a new password.

@Model.BaseUrl/account/resetpassword?token=@Model.User.PasswordResetToken

If you didn't try to reset your password, click the link below and we'll forget this ever happened.

@Model.BaseUrl/account/resetpassword?token=@Model.User.PasswordResetToken&cancel=true
